lead_paragraph: ALGIERS, Oct. 1 (AP) -- It still is uncertain where the Germans will make their next stand. It is obvious that they will attempt more delaying actions between Naples and Rome, 135 railway miles north.
abstract: Capt Sertorius repts on possible US 7th Army invasion
